        <div n="947B86L6" type="poem"><head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-947B86L6-headnote-1"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-947B86L6-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-947B86L6-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">B<hi rend="SMALL-CAPS">Y </hi>D<hi rend="SMALL-CAPS">EAN </hi>S<hi rend="SMALL-CAPS">WIFT</hi>.</l></lg></head><head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-947B86L6-headnote-2"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-947B86L6-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-947B86L6-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1">CATCH a 3 Voc.</l></lg></head><head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-947B86L6-headnote-3"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-947B86L6-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-947B86L6-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head>
      <lg n="1" type="stanza"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-947B86L6-line-1"> You always are making a God of your Spouse,&#13;</l><l n="2" xml:id="spp-947B86L6-line-2"> But this neither Reason nor Conscience allows;</l></lg><lg n="2" type="stanza"><l n="3" xml:id="spp-947B86L6-line-3">But·this·neither·Reason·nor·Conscience·allows;&#13;</l><l n="4" xml:id="spp-947B86L6-line-4"> Perhaps, you will say, 'tis in gratitude due,</l><l n="5" xml:id="spp-947B86L6-line-5"> And you adore him because he adores you,</l></lg><lg n="3" type="stanza"><l n="6" xml:id="spp-947B86L6-line-6">And·you·adore·him,·because·he·adores·you,&#13;</l><l n="7" xml:id="spp-947B86L6-line-7"> Your Argument's weak, and so you will find,</l><l n="8" xml:id="spp-947B86L6-line-8"> For you by this Rule, must adore all mankind,</l></lg><lg n="4" type="stanza"><l n="9" xml:id="spp-947B86L6-line-9">For·you·by·this·Rule,·must·adore· all·mankind.&#13;947B86L6   </l></lg></div>
